58.title: Episode #1.58
58.plot: El Chema orders a ceasefire against Ricardo, who wants to continue the war. Centeno?s disappearance is under investigation.

59.title: Episode #1.59
59.plot: Everything has to be ready once war is declared. Ricardo passes information to Fabrizio Ponce, who arrives in Sinaloa to catch El Chema dead or alive.

60.title: Episode #1.60
60.plot: El Chema shoots at the army and flees. Joaquín confronts Ponce and is shot. El Chema looks to Central America as a new route.

61.title: Episode #1.61
61.plot: El Chema allows Ponce to live and decides to attack the corrupt leaders. Joaquín and Elvira are given a new chance as a couple. Inés rejects Ricardo.

62.title: Episode #1.62
62.plot: A round table defines Ricardo Almenar as the common enemy. Imelda confronts El Chema. Fabrizio detains Clark and Marta for an inquiry.

63.title: Episode #1.63
63.plot: The drug enforcement agent has a witness and proof of movements that Tobías Clark can't justify.

64.title: Episode #1.64
64.plot: El Chema negotiates with Nelson and Tostao in order to find out and reduce Ricardo?s routes in Central America.

65.title: Episode #1.65
65.plot: After breaking up with Saúl, Amanda looks for el Chema. A single question raises suspicions. Nelson may use an event at the racetrack as his alibi.

66.title: Episode #1.66
66.plot: Nelson Martínez gets around the security tape and enters into Marta?s apartment, who is the key witness in the case against Tobías Clark.

67.title: Episode #1.67
67.plot: The drug business finally makes it to the 'big leagues' Nelson Martínez swears allegiance to el Chema. Clark feels miserable because he's a killer.

68.title: Episode #1.68
68.plot: El Chema expands his reach to flood Central America with drugs, and now counts on the CIA and death threats against Andrews.

69.title: Episode #1.69
69.plot: After losing a leg, Narváez uses Joaquín to exact his revenge. Meanwhile, Ponce and his men go to Sinaloa, where they are torturing Chema's father.

70.title: Episode #1.70
70.plot: Benito Narváez wants Chema to fall into the trap while he patiently waits for Joaquín. Meanwhile, Nelson flirts with Regina.

71.title: Episode #1.71
71.plot: El Chema surrounds Benito Narváez and those who protect him. Someone intervenes to stop the counterattack. Ricardo visits Tostao.

72.title: Episode #1.72
72.plot: Regina makes love to Nelson. Joaquín is laid to rest, and Chema swears to exact his revenge for his death.

73.title: Episode #1.73
73.plot: El Chema and his men attack Ricardo while he is meeting with Inés. The DEA and Ponce identify Marta's assassin.

74.title: Episode #1.74
74.plot: Blanca threatens the journalist who wrote negatively about Ricardo and her family. Tobías and his son find out that Inés was killed.

75.title: Episode #1.75
75.plot: Regina doesn't believe Rojo and Chema sows the seeds of doubt: Who got rid of Inés? Narváez makes a bribe and flees. Salma becomes Chema?s accomplice.

76.title: Episode #1.76
76.plot: Ponce frees Narváez and gets lynched. El Chema thinks he is the "world's best trafficker". Nelson wants to steal Regina. El Chema confronts him.

77.title: Episode #1.77
77.plot: El Chema convinces Philip to negotiate with him. Salma thanks El Chema for the appointment. Narváez collaborates. El Rojo wants to retire.

78.title: Episode #1.78
78.plot: Ricardo offers Nelson money to kill Regina and plots to finish off El Chema with Blanca. El Rojo is frightened for Regina. Amanda asks for a truce.

79.title: Episode #1.79
79.plot: Nelson flees with Regina. El Chema consolidates his business with help from the DEA and the CIA. Tobías goes after El Chema. Nelson is acting strange.

80.title: Episode #1.80
80.plot: Clark reveals that Almenar is responsible for the death of his wife. Selma tells Chema about Ponce?s intentions. El Chema and El Rojo go after Nelson.

81.title: Episode #1.81
81.plot: Nelson goes against Regina and her children. U.S. planes bomb El Chema's people. Selma agrees to sleep with Ponce for investigative purposes.

82.title: Episode #1.82
82.plot: El Rojo considers leaving the business. Ricardo claims responsibility for kidnapping Regina. El Chema and El Rojo order to have Blanca kidnapped.

83.title: Episode #1.83
83.plot: El Chema and El Rojo receive a special delivery. El Rojo goes crazy. Nelson is captured. El Chema tells Salma that he wants to retire.

84.title: Episode #1.84
84.plot: Ponce thwarts El Chema's operation. El Chema and El Rojo go after Ricardo. Blanca makes a deal with El Chema. Ponce traps Ricardo.

imdb.plot outline: Inspired by true events, This is the story of the most notorious drug kingpin the world had ever seen. A man known as El Chapo, the biggest international drug lord in history. The most important and influential man, in the history of Narcos. He changed the game with his spectacular escapes and innovative smuggling techniques.
